@startuml
title Campaign State Diagram

[*] --> Assignment
state Assignment
state Approval
state Preparation
state Scheduling
state Execution
state Extension
state Completion
state Payment
state FinalStatement
state Refund
state BalanceSettlement
state Paid
state Archive

Assignment --> Approval : assign manager and staff
Approval --> Preparation : contract signed / everything approved
Preparation --> Scheduling : prepare adverts
Scheduling --> Execution : approve and schedule adverts
Execution --> Extension : request extension / adjust campaign while running
Extension --> Execution
Completion --> FinalStatement : all adverts finished
FinalStatement --> Payment : generate final statement
Payment --> Refund : amount paid < required amount
Payment --> BalanceSettlement : amount paid > required amount
BalanceSettlement --> Paid : wait for correct balance to be settled
Paid --> Archive : mark campaign as paid
Archive --> [*] : release staff and managers / archive campaign
@enduml
